---
// Testimonials section with use case screenshots
---

<section class="px-4 md:px-20 py-20 md:py-32">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto space-y-12">
    <div class="text-center space-y-4">
      <span class="text-orange-500 font-semibold tracking-[0.2em] text-sm uppercase block">WHAT OUR CLIENTS SAY</span>
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl xl:text-7xl font-bold">Real Results. Real Businesses.</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-500 text-lg font-semibold max-w-2xl mx-auto">From AI search visibility to sovereign learning platforms, here is how European companies use Ironum.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8 pt-8">

      <!-- Testimonial 1: Helena Vossen — GEO / SEO -->
      <a href="/services/geo-optimization/" class="border-2 border-gray-100 rounded-2xl p-8 flex flex-col justify-between hover:border-blue-600 transition-all duration-200 no-underline">
        <div>
          <span class="inline-block bg-orange-500/10 text-orange-500 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider px-3 py-1 rounded-full mb-4">GEO Optimisation</span>
          <blockquote class="text-gray-700 text-base leading-relaxed mb-6">
            "Our competitors were getting recommended constantly and I couldn't figure out why. Our product was better, our site was faster. Turns out they had structured data and a stronger review footprint on the right platforms. The audit made it obvious. We fixed it in two weeks. Now we're in the recommendations alongside them."
          </blockquote>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4 pt-4 border-t border-gray-100">
          <img src="/avatars/helena-vossen.webp" alt="Helena Vossen" class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full object-cover" width="48" height="48" loading="lazy" />
          <div>
            <p class="font-bold text-gray-900">Helena Vossen</p>
            <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm">CEO @ smella.de</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <!-- Screenshot: askmention.com audit tool -->
        <div class="mt-6 rounded-xl overflow-hidden border border-gray-100">
          <img src="/screenshots/askmention.webp" alt="AskMention AI Presence Report showing visibility across ChatGPT, Gemini, Perplexity, Claude, and Copilot" class="w-full h-auto" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
      </a>

      <!-- Testimonial 2: Prof. Dr. Carsten Wolff — LLM Fine-Tuning -->
      <a href="/services/llm-fine-tuning/" class="border-2 border-gray-100 rounded-2xl p-8 flex flex-col justify-between hover:border-blue-600 transition-all duration-200 no-underline">
        <div>
          <span class="inline-block bg-orange-500/10 text-orange-500 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider px-3 py-1 rounded-full mb-4">LLM Fine-Tuning</span>
          <blockquote class="text-gray-700 text-base leading-relaxed mb-6">
            "We integrated quiz-based AI platform across multiple teaching methods, from inverted classrooms to quiz-based homework. The software boosted student motivation and helped them pass exams more successfully. It adapts seamlessly to individual learning needs, which is exactly what modern higher education demands."
          </blockquote>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4 pt-4 border-t border-gray-100">
          <img src="/avatars/carsten-wolff.png" alt="Prof. Dr. Carsten Wolff" class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full object-cover" width="48" height="48" loading="lazy" />
          <div>
            <p class="font-bold text-gray-900">Prof. Dr. Carsten Wolff</p>
            <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm">Board of Directors IDiAL, FH Dortmund</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <!-- Screenshot: FH Dortmund quiz library -->
        <div class="mt-6 rounded-xl overflow-hidden border border-gray-100">
          <img src="/screenshots/fh-dortmund.webp" alt="LearnSlice quiz library with SCRUM, orientation, and logistics courses at FH Dortmund" class="w-full h-auto" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
      </a>

      <!-- Testimonial 3: Alesia Kunz — Chatbot Interfaces -->
      <a href="/services/chatbot-interfaces/" class="border-2 border-gray-100 rounded-2xl p-8 flex flex-col justify-between hover:border-blue-600 transition-all duration-200 no-underline">
        <div>
          <span class="inline-block bg-orange-500/10 text-orange-500 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider px-3 py-1 rounded-full mb-4">Chatbot Interfaces</span>
          <blockquote class="text-gray-700 text-base leading-relaxed mb-6">
            "Our customers trust us with their data. When we needed AI-powered personalisation, we couldn't send student profiles to a US cloud. Ironum gave us a sovereign AI layer that runs entirely on European infrastructure. Our learners get a modern, personalised learning journey, and their data never leaves our control."
          </blockquote>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4 pt-4 border-t border-gray-100">
          <img src="/avatars/alesia-kunz.jpg" alt="Alesia Kunz" class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full object-cover" width="48" height="48" loading="lazy" />
          <div>
            <p class="font-bold text-gray-900">Alesia Kunz</p>
            <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm">CEO @ LearnSlice</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <!-- Screenshot: LearnSlice platform -->
        <div class="mt-6 rounded-xl overflow-hidden border border-gray-100">
          <img src="/screenshots/learnslice.webp" alt="LearnSlice AI learning platform with personalised learning modes and sovereign data processing" class="w-full h-auto" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
      </a>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>
